      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">4.2103</ph> Procedures.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d324e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Representations.</i>
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d324e17" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                     </p>
                     <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d324e22" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph> If the offeror
selects “does not” in response to the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-26.dita#id19CAC0P0ESS"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">52.204-26</xref> or <xref href="FAR-i1060550.dita#i1060550"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">52.212-3</xref>(v),
the contracting officer may rely on the representation, unless the
contracting officer has reason to question the representation. If the
contracting officer has a reason to question the representation,
the contracting officer shall follow agency procedures.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d324e33" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph> If the
offeror selects “does” in response to the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-26.dita#id19CAC0P0ESS"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">52.204-26</xref> or <xref href="FAR-i1060550.dita#i1060550"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">52.212-3</xref>(v),
the offeror must complete the representation at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                                    base="id1989I600I4C"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d324e47" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                     </p>
                     <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d324e52" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              <ph rev="FAC 2020-08 August 13, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2019-009?>If the offeror selects “will
not” in paragraph (d)(1) of the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                                       base="id1989I600I4C"
                                       outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref> or “does not”
in paragraph (d)(2) of the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                                       base="id1989I600I4C"
                                       outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>, the contracting
officer may rely on the representations, unless the contracting officer
has reason to question the representations. If the contracting officer
has a reason to question the representations, the contracting officer
shall follow agency procedures.<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 4.2103 by revising paragraph (a)(2).?></ph>
                           </p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d324e66" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              <ph rev="FAC 2020-08 August 13, 2020" class="- topic/ph ">If an offeror selects “will”
in paragraph (d)(1) of the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                                       base="id1989I600I4C"
                                       outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>, the offeror
must provide the information required by paragraph (e)(1) of the
provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                                       base="id1989I600I4C"
                                       outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>,
and the contracting officer shall follow agency procedures.</ph>
                           </p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="d324e78" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              <ph rev="FAC 2020-08 August 13, 2020" class="- topic/ph ">If
an offeror selects “does” in paragraph (d)(2) of the provision at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                                       base="id1989I600I4C"
                                       outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>, the offeror
must complete the disclosure at paragraph (e)(2) of the provision
at <xref href="FAR-52.204-24.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                                       base="id1989I600I4C"
                                       outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">52.204-24</xref>,
and the contracting officer shall follow agency procedures.</ph>
                           </p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d324e90" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Reporting</i>.
If a contractor provides a report pursuant to paragraph (d) of the
clause at <xref href="FAR-52.204-25.dita#id1989I600I4C"
                        base="id1989I600I4C"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.204-25</xref>,
Prohibition on Contracting for Certain Telecommunications and Video
Surveillance Services or Equipment, follow agency procedures.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
